# Law - Domain Concepts
# Foundational legal concepts with proper graph semantics

# Domain anchor (avoid free-floating atoms)
@_:Law isA Law AbstractType

# ===== Legal Entities =====

@Law:Law graph legalrule
    # Legal rule or statute
    @r __Role Theme $legalrule
    @type __Role Type Law
    @ctx __Role Context Law
    @concept __Bundle $ctx $r $type
    return $concept
end

